explains: n. 时间轴，时间线；大事年表

sentences.en: That now seems an impossible timeline.
sentences.cn: 现在看来，这似乎是一个不可能的时间表。

sentences.en: The timeline has a line divided in equal parts.
sentences.cn: 时间线有一条等分的线。

sentences.en: A timeline is an ordered group of words and dates that shows when events happened.
sentences.cn: 时间轴是单词和日期的有序组，显示事件发生的时间。
